scenes.description: Mori Calliope interacts with the Hololive Myth members while standing on a fiery hell-themed stage.
Amelia Watson requests Calliope to do 'the worm' dance move, which she eventually performs.
Takanashi Kiara requests the 'Caramelldansen' dance, and Calliope performs it while worried about copyrights.
Gawr Gura requests a cartwheel and an action roll, which Calliope attempts in 3D.
Ninomae Ina'nis prepares to make a final request for Calliope to do something 'cute'.
